#: ../../installation.rst:130
msgid "Java options"
msgstr "Java-Optionen"

#: ../../installation.rst:131
msgid ""
"There are some Java options that need to be configured before starting the "
"Tomcat server. These options are configured using the ``JAVA_OPTS`` "
"environment variable. It should contain the following values:"
msgstr ""
"Die folgenden Java-Optionen müssen über die ``JAVA_OPTS`` Umgebungsvariable "
"gesetzt werden, bevor Tomcat gestartet wird:"

#: ../../installation.rst:136
msgid "``-Xms1536m``"
msgstr "``-Xms1536m``"

#: ../../installation.rst:136
msgid "minimum RAM, should be at least 1.5GB"
msgstr "minimaler RAM, sollte mindestens 1.5GB betragen"

#: ../../installation.rst:138
msgid "``-Xmx2048m``"
msgstr "``-Xmx2048m``"

#: ../../installation.rst:138
msgid "maximum RAM, should be at least 2GB but more is recommended"
msgstr ""
"maximaler RAM, sollte mindestens 2GB betragen, mehr ist jedoch empfehlenswert"

#: ../../installation.rst:140
msgid "``-Dfile.encoding=UTF-8``"
msgstr "``-Dfile.encoding=UTF-8``"

#: ../../installation.rst:140
msgid "sets UTF-8 as Apache Tomcat’s default encoding mechanism"
msgstr "setzt UTF-8 als den Standard-Encodingsmechanismus des Apache Tomcats"

#: ../../installation.rst:142
msgid "``-XX:PermSize=128m``"
msgstr "``-XX:PermSize=128m``"

#: ../../installation.rst:142
msgid "initial permanent generation space in MB"
msgstr "initialer “Permantent Generation Space” in MB"

#: ../../installation.rst:144
msgid "``-XX:MaxPermSize=256m``"
msgstr "``-XX:MaxPermSize=256m``"

#: ../../installation.rst:144
msgid "maximum permanent generation space in MB"
msgstr "maximaler “Permantent Generation Space” in MB"

#: ../../installation.rst:147
msgid ""
"In order to allocate sufficient RAM to the Tomcat server you have to set the "
"``Xms`` and ``Xmx`` options, followed by the number of MB allocated and a "
"literal ``m``. ``Xms`` defines the initial/minimum amount of RAM that is "
"used and ``Xmx`` the allowed maximum. You are advised to allocate at least "
"2GB of RAM to the Tomcat. However, it is recommended to use more RAM. For "
"example, if you want to assign 4GB of maximum RAM the option would be ``-"
"Xmx4096m``\\ ."
msgstr ""
"Um ausreichend RAM für Tomcat zur Verfügung zu stellen, müssen die ``Xms`` "
"und ``Xmx``\\ -Optionen gesetzt werden, gefolgt von der MB-Anzahl und dem "
"Buchstaben ``m``\\ . ``Xms`` definiert den minimalen RAM, ``Xmx`` den "
"maximalen RAM. Es sollten mindestens 2GB RAM zugewiesen werden, mehr ist "
"jedoch empfehlenswert. Wenn Sie z.B. 4GB maximalen RAM zuweisen möchten, "
"würde die Option wie folgt aussehen: ``-Xmx4096m``"

#: ../../installation.rst:152
msgid ""
"The values for the permanent generation space have to be increased as well, "
"these are defined by the values ``-XX:PermSize=128m`` and ``-XX:"
"MaxPermSize=256m``\\ ."
msgstr ""
"Zudem müssen die Werte für den “Permantent Generation Space” erhöht werden. "
"Hierfür sind die Variablen ``-XX:PermSize=128m`` und ``-XX:"
"MaxPermSize=256m`` zu setzen."

#: ../../installation.rst:156
msgid ""
"If you installed Tomcat using the Windows service installer, you can open "
"the configuration dialog by opening the Windows start menu and selecting "
"``Program Files\\Apache Tomcat\\Configure Tomcat``\\ ."
msgstr ""
"Falls Sie Tomcat über den Windows Installer installiert haben, öffnen Sie "
"nun den Konfigurationsdialog über das ``Startmenü und Programme\\Apache "
"Tomcat\\Configure Tomcat``\\ . "

#: ../../installation.rst:162
msgid "The Java tab of the Tomcat configuration dialog"
msgstr "Das Java-Tab in Tomcats Konfigurationsdialog"

#: ../../installation.rst:164
msgid ""
"The tab Java offers the possibility to set the options and define the memory "
"pool (minimum and maximum RAM usage). Fill in the values for Xms and Xmx "
"into the fields for memory pool and add the other options to the text area "
"labeled as Java Options."
msgstr ""
"Das \"Java-Tab\" ermöglicht es nun, die entsprechenden Optionen zu setzen. "
"Minimaler und maximaler RAM-Zuweisung werden unter “Initial memory pool” und "
"“Maximum memory pool” definiert. Fügen Sie die verbleibenden Option in das "
"Textfeld \"Java Options\" ein."

