msgid ""
"MongoDB is currently the only database system that Signavio Workflow "
"supports. If you already have an infrastructure that can provide a MongoDB "
"version 3.2.x instance, simply create a new instance for Signavio Workflow "
"and skip to :ref:`configure-mongodb`. Otherwise continue with the "
"installation instructions."
msgstr ""
